# xarray-regrid
Regridding utility for xarray.

## Installation

```console
pip install xarray-regrid
```

## Usage & benchmarks
To see how to use xarray-regrid, see the benchmark notebooks. These also contain a comparison to more standard methods (CDO, xESMF).
